                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pekin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-10-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 25, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>(Received via Taku, 26.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger states that the reported intention to remove Yangtze viceroys is said
                    by Li to be untrue.)</p>
            </div>
